Daniel Olukoya of the General Overseer of the Mountain of Fire and Miracles Ministries, has released prophecies for the year 2022. Olukoya urged Nigerians to pray against inflation and starvation. He called for prayers against political instability in the year 2022. Speaking during MFM’s crossover service, Olukoya said Nigerians should pray against strange deaths. According to Olukoya: “We need to pray against inflation and starvation. “We need to pray against massive political instability, which will put a lot of people in disarray. “We need to pray against strange deaths. “The church needs prayers against increased persecution of Christians. “The God of the ‘suddenlies’ is preparing something for Nigeria and will answer the prayers of His children. “For any power that wants Nigeria to sink shall sink, and any power that wants Nigeria to die shall die; they will drink their own blood and eat their own flesh, until they are drunk with it.”